{quote}
We are currently building a portal to gather monthly some interesting indicators regarding our Cloud products (including our Atlassian Cloud products). It is to know (on a montly/annualy base for example) their usage, their availability, the performance data related, etc. {quote}

It would definitely help them in gathering the indicator in the form of monthly statistics to address their business need.

h3. Issue Summary
User type Content Property Index Extraction not working. An extraction with valueType {{user}} no longer appears in Content by Label macro

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Create an extraction of valueType user like {code}{
  "objectName": "state.approvers",
  "type": "string",
  "alias": "approver",
  "uiSupport": {
    "defaultOperator": "=",
    "name": {
      "value": "Assigned approver"
    },
    "tooltip": {
      "value": "User assigned to review the page"
    },
    "valueType": "user"
  }
}{code}
# Add a _Content by Label_ macro
# Add a filter and search for the extraction with uiSupport.

h3. Expected Results
In content by label macro the app defined user filter should appear

h3. Actual Results
In content by label macro the filter doesn't appear

h3. Workaround
Currently there is no known workaround for this behavior. A workaround will be added here when available.

